Ten-hut.

268
00:27:29,530 --> 00:27:31,158
- Carry on. - Carry on.

269
00:27:32,933 --> 00:27:33,888
This it?

270
00:27:34,101 --> 00:27:35,033
Yes, sir.

271
00:27:35,302 --> 00:27:36,599
Our new radar.

272
00:27:36,804 --> 00:27:38,465
It's a remarkable scientific achievement...

273
00:27:38,672 --> 00:27:40,794
