274
00:27:40,808 --> 00:27:42,993
...and at quite a range.

275
00:27:43,176 --> 00:27:44,801
Now, listen, colonel, as you know,

276
00:27:44,945 --> 00:27:47,743
we're short on patrol planes.

277
00:27:48,048 --> 00:27:53,475
We're gonna have to rely on this...thing to detect the enemy.

278
00:27:53,821 --> 00:27:56,483
