312
00:29:51,205 --> 00:29:52,001
not you.

313
00:29:55,843 --> 00:29:58,368
I must get back to the fleet.

314
00:29:58,579 --> 00:30:01,776
There is a lot to be done.

315
00:30:06,553 --> 00:30:09,249
It's no use, Hal. I spoke to General Miles.

316
00:30:09,456 --> 00:30:11,412
He took it up with General Marshall.

317
00:30:11,725 --> 00:30:13,317
The order stands.

318
00:30:13,727 --> 00:30:16,855
