They hit one plane, and it all goes up in flames.

372
00:34:05,426 --> 00:34:07,651
I'm sorry. General's orders.

373
00:34:52,005 --> 00:34:55,031
Today's war games...

374
00:34:55,383 --> 00:34:58,261
...of a theoretical attack on Pearl Harbor...

375
00:34:58,545 --> 00:35:04,711
...clearly show the need for six carriers in the attack force.

376
00:35:04,985 --> 00:35:08,347
The General Staff...

377
00:35:08,689 --> 00:35:13,420
...wants to limit us to only three carriers.

378
00:35:13,861 --> 00:35:16,022
We must have six!

379
00:35:19,166 --> 00:35:20,423
lf we reduce our striking force...

380
00:35:20,469 --> 00:35:23,870
...from six carriers to only three...

381
00:35:24,938 --> 00:35:26,701
...our mission will fail.

382
00:35:27,241 --> 00:35:29,004
Before attacking anything else,

383
00:35:29,076 --> 00:35:31,465
we should attack our General Staff.

384
00:35:33,916 --> 00:35:37,775
We believe in aircraft,

385
00:35:38,185 --> 00:35:42,508
but they cling to the ancient theory...

386
00:35:42,723 --> 00:35:45,146
...that decisive naval engagements must be fought between battleships.

387
00:35:45,359 --> 00:35:47,987
Unless we dispel this myth...

388
00:35:48,562 --> 00:35:52,419
...we'll never get their approval.

389
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,986
They are not the only believers in the "battleship theory."

390
00:35:55,235 --> 00:35:57,629
Many officers here today also support the idea.

391
00:35:58,872 --> 00:36:00,271
I'm one of them.

392
00:36:00,974 --> 00:36:04,332
We'll soon have two new unsinkable battlewagons...

393
00:36:04,745 --> 00:36:09,269
...each with a displacement of 64,000 tons and huge guns.

394
00:36:09,449 --> 00:36:11,672
Anything that floats can be sunk!

395
00:36:11,885 --> 00:36:13,443
The "unsinkable" ship is a myth.

396
00:36:13,671 --> 00:36:16,778
The war in Europe is being decided by the airplane.

397
00:36:17,024 --> 00:36:19,720
There can be no victory on land or sea,

398
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,217
without control of the air!

399
00:36:21,789 --> 00:36:25,281
I have been chosen to command this task force.

400
00:36:25,793 --> 00:36:28,091
And l consider this operation risky.

401
00:36:28,295 --> 00:36:30,786
How can we travel 3500 miles to Hawaii without being detected?

402
00:36:32,767 --> 00:36:36,291
This mission will fail unless we achieve complete surprise.

403
00:36:37,304 --> 00:36:39,670
My ships can't carry fuel for a trip there and back.

404
00:36:40,007 --> 00:36:44,296
Stopping to refuel increases the possibility of detection.

405
00:36:44,545 --> 00:36:45,375
That's enough

406
00:36:46,113 --> 00:36:51,572
I am confident that our ships will reach Hawaii safely.

407
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:54,811
You are too cautious.

408
00:36:54,989 --> 00:36:57,150
The case for using six carriers is sound.

409
00:36:57,524 --> 00:37:00,816
To criticize the plan is defeatist!

410
00:37:18,145 --> 00:37:24,311
No more bickering! As long as l am Commander-in-Chief...

411
00:37:25,552 --> 00:37:28,112
...Pearl Harbor will be attacked!

412
00:37:31,832 --> 00:37:35,123
I am aware that this is a dangerous gamble.

413
00:37:35,863 --> 00:37:38,593
But we can't afford the luxury of playing it safe now!

414
00:37:45,406 --> 00:37:48,000
Gentlemen, whether we adopt this plan or not...

415
00:37:48,242 --> 00:37:49,732
is no longer an issue.

416
00:37:50,184 --> 00:37:54,006
Let us now decide how best to carry it out.

417
00:38:10,230 --> 00:38:12,892
Fuchida's back! Fuchida's back!

418
00:38:19,039 --> 00:38:21,234
Fuchida! What a surprise!

419
00:38:21,675 --> 00:38:23,370
I'm your new Air Commander,

420
00:38:23,610 --> 00:38:24,770
so treat me well.

421
00:38:25,446 --> 00:38:27,209
You're joking.

422
00:38:27,281 --> 00:38:29,545
How did you rate another promotion?

423
00:38:29,890 --> 00:38:33,875
Well, exceptional people get exceptional treatment!

424
00:38:39,059 --> 00:38:40,424


425
00:38:44,598 --> 00:38:47,453
