00:41:31,464 --> 00:41:33,796
...so they know what to do with the information.

448
00:41:34,067 --> 00:41:35,432
Take it easy, Murph.

449
00:41:35,635 --> 00:41:40,098
- You'll figure it out. - Yeah, I'll figure it out.

450
00:41:43,877 --> 00:41:45,333
Don't just stand there.

451
00:41:45,578 --> 00:41:47,307
You know how to operate this thing.

452
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:48,569
We know the theory.

453
00:41:48,815 --> 00:41:50,840
Let's put that theory into practice.

454
00:41:50,917 --> 00:41:52,045
- Switch on. - Yes, sir.

455
00:41:56,256 --> 00:41:58,850
Stay put and keep watching the screen.

456
00:41:59,092 --> 00:42:00,753
ln two hours, close down.

457
00:42:00,927 --> 00:42:02,224
I'll send a truck to pick you up.

458
00:42:02,929 --> 00:42:03,918
Excuse me, sir,

459
00:42:04,130 --> 00:42:05,757
but what are we watching for?

460
00:42:05,932 --> 00:42:09,234
Anything unusual.  Any large blip coming from the sea.

461
00:42:09,235 --> 00:42:11,692
Colonel, if we do spot something,

462
00:42:11,838 --> 00:42:12,664
what do we do?

463
00:42:12,746 --> 00:42:15,164
Report it to headquarters, damn it.

464
00:42:15,408 --> 00:42:16,904
- How, sir? - What?

465
00:42:17,410 --> 00:42:19,475
