478
00:43:11,864 --> 00:43:13,630
Just sit tight.

479
00:43:13,965 --> 00:43:15,383
Listen for the phone. That's all.

480
00:43:15,835 --> 00:43:17,666
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

481
00:43:25,678 --> 00:43:28,909
Haleiwa is one of the subsidiary fields.

482
00:43:29,072 --> 00:43:31,899
We send those two up there,

483
00:43:31,983 --> 00:43:33,106
two more here.

484
00:43:33,319 --> 00:43:35,651
Only way l know to disperse a few of the planes.

485
00:43:39,692 --> 00:43:40,818
lf I'd get away with it,

486
00:43:40,994 --> 00:43:43,622
I'd send all to the neighbor islands.

487
00:43:43,963 --> 00:43:45,828
You know why we're being transferred.

488
00:43:45,999 --> 00:43:47,398
Them poker games.

489
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:49,327
Been winning too often.

490
00:43:49,569 --> 00:43:50,729
Yeah.

