...believe that America is a nation divided, isolationist...

559
00:48:24,346 --> 00:48:29,920
and that Americans are only interested in enjoying a life of

560
00:48:29,920 --> 00:48:35,494
luxury and are spiritually and morally corrupt.

561
00:48:36,990 --> 00:48:38,756
But that is a great mistake.

562
00:48:40,860 --> 00:48:43,055
lf war becomes inevitable...

563
00:48:44,363 --> 00:48:50,893
...America would be the most formidable foe that we have ever fought.

564
