Now we've lost them.

731
01:03:03,458 --> 01:03:07,383
Look, Rufe, try to put yourself in their minds.

732
01:03:07,796 --> 01:03:11,618
Where do you think l have been the past week, night and day?

733
01:03:12,834 --> 01:03:16,133
I am still convinced they're going to attack us.

734
01:03:17,973 --> 01:03:21,898
What can we do that we aren't doing already?

735
01:03:22,144 --> 01:03:23,441
I don't know about you,

736
01:03:23,712 --> 01:03:25,168
but l know what I'm gonna do.

737
01:03:27,149 --> 01:03:28,600
Where is everybody?

738
01:03:28,617 --> 01:03:31,750
Oh, it's past 12, sir. They've already gone.

739
01:03:31,919 --> 01:03:33,961
- Get them back. - On the weekend?

740
01:03:34,122 --> 01:03:35,384
Yes, on the weekend.

741
