Right.

776
01:06:29,231 --> 01:06:30,960
You're late.

777
01:06:31,166 --> 01:06:33,755
- Well, l was-- - Please, take me to the White House.

778
01:06:44,746 --> 01:06:46,771
lf you told me we were invited to the White House,

779
01:06:47,148 --> 01:06:48,137
l would've dressed.

780
01:06:50,652 --> 01:06:52,176
You know Mrs. Roosevelt.

781
01:06:52,354 --> 01:06:54,083
She's informal personally,

782
01:06:54,256 --> 01:06:55,780
but a stickler for protocol--

783
01:06:56,024 --> 01:06:58,288
Darling, will you shut up and drive?

784
01:07:37,699 --> 01:07:38,893
Once more!

785
01:07:46,924 --> 01:07:59,780
Steady.

786
01:08:02,190 --> 01:08:07,151
Great! We just sank the Nevada!

787
01:08:13,301 --> 01:08:14,325
Pennsylvania!

