Mr. Secretary.

1214
02:04:40,518 --> 02:04:43,510
"Air raid. Pearl Harbor. This is no drill."

1215
02:04:44,522 --> 02:04:46,424
No, this can't be true.

1216
02:04:46,998 --> 02:04:48,590
They must mean the Philippines.

1217
02:04:48,759 --> 02:04:50,124
No, sir.

1218
02:04:50,328 --> 02:04:51,727
It's Pearl.

1219
02:04:54,165 --> 02:04:56,531
Get me the White House, the direct line.

1220
02:04:56,701 --> 02:04:57,599
Yes, sir.

1221
02:05:03,474 --> 02:05:05,635
Mr. Ambassador, Mr. Hull will see you in a moment.

1222
