1296
02:20:57,592 --> 02:21:00,322
Since we don't know where they are...

1297
02:21:00,495 --> 02:21:01,484
...we can't use our ...

1298
02:21:01,562 --> 02:21:03,826
limited supply of fuel to look for them.

1299
02:21:05,600 --> 02:21:10,196
We must not forget that enemy submarines will be searching for us.

1300
02:21:12,340 --> 02:21:14,433
